<h1 id="the-tempest">The Tempest</h1>

<h2 id="text-encoding">Text Encoding</h2>

<p>How has the text evolved from when it was originally written to the online version?</p>

<p>The production of our Tempest edition</p>
<ul>
  <li>1611 play is performed, circulates in manuscript</li>
  <li>1623 First Folio</li>
  <li>Print Folger editions (synthetic)</li>
  <li>TEI edition</li>
  <li>Web edition</li>
</ul>

<h2 id="context">Context</h2>
<p>Inspired by a true ship reck</p>

<p><strong>The Great Chain of Being:</strong> Represents the hierarchy of things during the time of Shakespeare</p>
<ul>
  <li>God</li>
  <li>Angles</li>
  <li>Humans</li>
  <li>Beast</li>
  <li>Plant</li>
  <li>Flame</li>
  <li>Stone</li>
</ul>

