      <span class="nt">&lt;l&gt;</span>Spirits to enforce: Art to inchant,<span class="nt">&lt;/l&gt;</span>
      <span class="nt">&lt;l&gt;</span>And my ending is despaire,<span class="nt">&lt;/l&gt;</span>
      <span class="nt">&lt;l&gt;</span>Vnlesse I be relieu'd by praier<span class="nt">&lt;/l&gt;</span>
      <span class="nt">&lt;l&gt;</span>Which pierces so, that it assaults<span class="nt">&lt;/l&gt;</span>
